# =============================================================================
# USAGE INSTRUCTIONS
# =============================================================================

# 1. Copy this file: cp environment_variables.template .env
# 2. Edit .env with your actual values
# 3. Source the file before running Informatica: source .env
# 4. Ensure .env is in your .gitignore file
# 5. Use these variables in your parameter files and connection strings

